summary: Horns and Feathers show through helmets. For those, like me, that have problems with Horns Are Forever. Horns and Feathers cannot be seen through Full Face Helmets.
descriptionHtml:
Horns and Feathers show through helmets. For those, like me, that have problems with Horns Are Forever. Horns and Feathers cannot be seen through Full Face Helmets.

Recommened Mod: Improved Closefaced Helmets by Navida1 (http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15927)
Allows horns and feathers to be seen through full face helmets.

Place as close to last as possible in Load Order.
author: AurinZalas
